---

## Step 5: North Star Metric

Define a single North Star Metric that captures the core value delivered to customers.

**Requirements:**
1. Directly tied to customer value
2. Measurable
3. Actionable
4. Predictive of long-term success

**Format (up to 60 words):**

> For [target customer] with [problem], we propose [solution]. Our primary goal is [Product Goal]. We will know we're successful when [main KPI metric reaches target].

**Example:**
> For remote teams with scattered work and unclear priorities, we propose TaskFlow's async-first workspace. Our primary goal is to increase activation rate to 60%. We will know we're successful when 60% of new users complete their first project within 7 days.

